&quot;After being unseen for at least one second, your next basic attack against an enemy champion does 45-300 bonus damage.&quot; Meaning, when you Tumble with Vayne ult, not only do you get the extra 50 AD when your ult is popped, but you also get the Bonus AD from your Q proc. AKA, you can one shot a squishy target 5 times because you can continuously proc Duskblade for it has no cooldown on its passive. Imagine a build like this:

{{item:3147}} {{item:3087}} {{item:3031}} {{item:3006}} {{item:3142}} {{item:3153}} 

She already hit&#039;s me for 2/3 of my health with one Q Ult auto with {{item:3031}} {{item:3087}}, let alone her getting that extra 300 bonus damage every second when she Tumbles. Riot, for the love of fucking Christ, but a cooldown on the passive.
